commit.message:
Add viewer count, last visit geotag, and live feed polish on home page

- main.py: track view_clients (home page WS connections) for viewer count;
  record last visitor location via ip-api.com geo lookup on view connect;
  expose viewers + last_location in /status response
- home.html: open role=view WebSocket on load to register as viewer;
  show live viewer count (👀 watching: N) overlaid bottom-left of stream;
  show most recent visit location (🌐) below nav, hidden until first result;
  replace corner brackets on stream with full teal border + glow;
  scanlines excluded from stream via z-index layering;
  remove "draw something" tagline; fix hint text line break

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
